        "type": "path",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Two Actions\" aria-label=\"Two Actions\">1</span></p><p><em>You assume a flexible stance, allowing you to quickly switch between inexorable advances and rapid reactions to wear down your foe.</em></p><p>Your Physical and Cognitive defenses increase by 1. Additionally, after you’re hit or grazed by a melee attack, you can use <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Two Actions\" aria-label=\"Two Actions\">r</span> to make an <strong>Athletics</strong> test against your attacker’s Cognitive defense. On a success, your target loses [[/r 1d4]] focus, and you can push them horizontally up to 5 feet × your ranks in <strong>Athletics</strong>.</p>",
            "chat": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Two Actions\" aria-label=\"Two Actions\">1</span></p><p>Enter Vinestance: Your Physical and Cognitive defenses increase by 1. After you’re hit or grazed in melee, spend <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Two Actions\" aria-label=\"Two Actions\">r</span> to test <strong>Athletics</strong> vs. Cognitive to make attacker lose [[/r 1d4]] focus and be pushed.</p>",
            "short": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Two Actions\" aria-label=\"Two Actions\">1</span></p><p>Your Physical and Cognitive defenses increase by 1. Additionally, after you’re hit or grazed by a melee attack, you can use <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Two Actions\" aria-label=\"Two Actions\">r</span> to make an <strong>Athletics</strong> test against your attacker’s Cognitive defense. On a success, your target loses [[/r 1d4]] focus, and you can push them horizontally up to 5 feet × your ranks in <strong>Athletics</strong>.</p>"
